WEBVTT

00:00:02.106 --> 00:00:03.984
To most of you, this is a device

00:00:03.984 --> 00:00:06.992
to buy, sell, play games,

00:00:06.992 --> 00:00:08.902
watch videos.

00:00:08.902 --> 00:00:11.042
I think it might be a lifeline.

00:00:11.042 --> 00:00:13.458
I think actually it might be able to save more lives

00:00:13.458 --> 00:00:14.958
than penicillin.

00:00:14.958 --> 00:00:16.431
Texting:

00:00:16.431 --> 00:00:19.250
I know I say texting and a lot of you think sexting,

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:22.500
a lot of you think about the lewd photos that you see --

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:25.125
hopefully not your kids sending to somebody else --

00:00:25.125 --> 00:00:26.917
or trying to translate the abbreviations

00:00:26.917 --> 00:00:29.875
LOL, LMAO, HMU.

00:00:29.875 --> 00:00:31.708
I can help you with those later.